                <p id="vpara" >   
                         Impart quality professional education, skills and values through outcome-based innovative teaching <br>learning process in all spheres.
                        <br> Udertake collaborative interdisciplinary research as a co-requisite for professional education and <br>simultaneously solve problems faced by society and industry.
                        <br> Create an ambience of innovation, entrepreneurship and consultancy for future leaders and innovators.
                        <br> Keep faculty members enthusiastic by continuous professional development and positive working <br>environment.
                    </ul>
                </p>

